{"tid":2052692,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英美等8國及歐洲議會政界組聯盟應對中國　城大學生會副會長任顧問","createTime":"2020-06-05T17:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T20:14:05.000Z","uid":39464,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b2f5b0cf5fe073e83cbe25de6b1949b01698f6e7","tid":2052692,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T17:03:05.000Z","msg":"多國資深國會議員及政界人士今日（5日）宣布組成「對華政策跨國議會聯盟」（IPAC），以協調民主國家之間的對策，應對中國帶來的挑戰，並會關注香港議題。<br />\n<br />\n聯盟現有18名聯席主席，分別來自英國、美國、澳洲、加拿大、德國、日本、挪威、瑞典8個國家以及歐洲議會，各有兩名代表不同黨派成員參與。聯盟由英國保守黨前黨魁施志安（Iain Duncan Smith）發起，其他成員包括美國參議員魯比奧（Marco Rubio）和梅南德茲（Robert Menendez）、日本前防衛大臣中谷元等。聯盟官方網頁顯示，團隊亦設11名顧問，包括香港城市大學學生會外務副會長邵嵐。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200605/s00005/1591356248005/%e8%8b%b1%e7%be%8e%e7%ad%898%e5%9c%8b%e5%8f%8a%e6%ad%90%e6%b4%b2%e8%ad%b0%e6%9c%83%e6%94%bf%e7%95%8c%e7%b5%84%e8%81%af%e7%9b%9f%e6%87%89%e5%b0%8d%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b-%e5%9f%8e%e5%a4%a7%e5%ad%b8%e7%94%9f%e6%9c%83%e5%89%af%e6%9c%83%e9%95%b7%e4%bb%bb%e9%a1%a7%e5%95%8f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200605%2Fs00005%2F1591356248005%2F%25e8%258b%25b1%25e7%25be%258e%25e7%25ad%25898%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%258f%258a%25e6%25ad%2590%25e6%25b4%25b2%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%2594%25bf%25e7%2595%258c%25e7%25b5%2584%25e8%2581%25af%25e7%259b%259f%25e6%2587%2589%25e5%25b0%258d%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b-%25e5%259f%258e%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e7%2594%259f%25e6%259c%2583%25e5%2589%25af%25e6%259c%2583%25e9%2595%25b7%25e4%25bb%25bb%25e9%25a1%25a7%25e5%2595%258f&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGedFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=eb14aba1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200605%2Fs00005%2F1591356248005%2F%25e8%258b%25b1%25e7%25be%258e%25e7%25ad%25898%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%258f%258a%25e6%25ad%2590%25e6%25b4%25b2%25e8%25ad%25b0%2